 a_{n+1}-a_n=\frac{\sqrt{2+\sqrt{3+\cdots\sqrt{n+1}}}-\sqrt{2+\sqrt{3+\cdots\sqrt{n}}}}{a_{n+1}+a_n}\\ \leq\frac{\sqrt{2+\sqrt{3+\cdots\sqrt{n+1}}}-\sqrt{2+\sqrt{3+\cdots\sqrt{n}}}}{2}\\ =\frac12\,\frac{\sqrt{3+\sqrt{4+\cdots\sqrt{n+1}}}-\sqrt{3+\sqrt{4+\cdots\sqrt{n}}}}{\sqrt{2+\sqrt{3+\cdots\sqrt{n+1}}}+\sqrt{2+\sqrt{3+\cdots\sqrt{n}}}}\\ \leq\frac12\,\frac{\sqrt{3+\sqrt{4+\cdots\sqrt{n+1}}}-\sqrt{3+\sqrt{4+\cdots\sqrt{n}}}}{2\sqrt2}\\ \leq\cdots\\ \leq\frac{\sqrt{n+1}}{2^{n+1}}\leq\frac{n+1}{2^n} 
 a_{n+k}-a_n=\sum_{j=1}^ka_{n+j}-a_{n+j-1}\leq\sum_{j=1}^k\frac{n+j+1}{2^{n+j}}\leq\frac3{2^n}. 
